confOf#Trip: The social event is the parent of the trip and the working event. The Administrative event is the parent of the trip and the Social event is also the parent of the trip.
confOf#Banquet: The Social Event is the parent of the Banquet. The Social Event is also the child of the Administrative event which is parallel to the Administrative event. The Submission event is also a child of the Social event.
confOf#Reception: Reception is the parent of Social event which is a child of Trip and Reception.
confOf#Social_event: Social event is a child of Banquet and is the parent of Banquet. It is the default choice.
confOf#Event: The Social Event is the parent of the Conference and the Banquet. It is also the child of the Social event which is also the child of the Banquet. The Banquet is also the child of the Conference.
confOf#Contribution: The hasTitle of Contribution is Thing.
confOf#City: The following table shows the percentage of people who are enrolled in the program.
confOf#Organization: The City University is the parent of the City Organization which is a child of the University.
confOf#Person: The administrator is the parent of the person who is a member of the PC. The administrator is also the child of the person who is an expert on the topic.
confOf#Topic: The following table shows the percentage of people who are enrolled in the program.
confOf#Country: The following table shows the percentage of people who are enrolled in the program.
confOf#Company: The parent of the company is the organization which is the child of the company and the parent of the organization is the university.
confOf#University: The University is the parent of the organization hasCity which is in the country.
confOf#Scholar: The parent of a person who is studying at the University is the person who is the parent of the organization which is the parent of the company which is the parent of the company which is the city of hasCity. The organization is also the parent of the company which is the parent of the company which is the city of hasCity.
confOf#Administrator: The administrator is the parent of the person who is the child of the Science Worker and the Assistant.
confOf#Poster: The Poster is the parent of the Thing and the Contribution.
confOf#Paper: The author of the Poster is the parent of the Poster which is written by the author. The Poster is also the child of the member of the PC and the person who wrote it is the parent of the Thing.
confOf#Short_paper: Short paper is the parent of Contribution which is a child of Short paper. ContactEmail is the source of the contribution.
confOf#Reviewing_results_event: Reviewing results is the parent event of Administrative event which is a parallel event with Administrative event.
confOf#Administrative_event: The Administrative event is the child of the Camera Ready event and the Submission event.
confOf#Reviewing_event: Reviewing event is parented by both Administrative event and Working event. Working event is a child of both Administrative event and Tutorial event.
confOf#Registration_of_participants_even: The registration of participants event is parented by both the Administrative event and the Social event. Reviewing event is a child of the Administrative event and the Conference is also a child of the Social event.
confOf#Submission_event: The Submission event is parented by the Administrative event, which is also the parent of the Social event, which is also the parent of the Reviewing results event. The Social event is also the parent of the Banquet.
confOf#Camera_Ready_event: The Camera Ready event is the parent of the Administrative event which is followed by the Working event. The Social event is also the parent of the Banquet and Conference events.
confOf#Workshop: Working event is parented by Conference and Administrative event. Workshop is parented by Administrative event and Conference is parented by Working event.
confOf#Conference: Working event is a child of Conference and Tutorial.
confOf#Tutorial: Working event is parented by an event which has a topic. It is also a child of a social event which is located at Thing.
confOf#Working_event: The Conference is the parent event of the Working event. The Social event is the parent event of the Conference. Registration of participants is the event's follow up event.
confOf#Member: The parent of a participant is the parent of a regular person who is employed by a company. The regular person is a member of the organization and the company is a child of the University.
confOf#Participant: The Participant is the parent of the student and the Chair PC. The Chair PC is the parent of the student and the Participant is the child of the Thing.
confOf#Member_PC: Member PC reviewes Contribution which is a child of Paper and Short paper. Member PC is an expert on this topic.
confOf#Chair_PC: Chair PC is the parent of Person who is the child of Chair PC and is the parent of Thing.
confOf#Student: The student is the parent of the participant and the child of the member. The member is the parent of Thing and the student is the child of the participant.
confOf#Science_Worker: The Science Worker is the child of the Administrator and the parent of the Science Worker.
confOf#Assistant: The Assistant is the parent of the child of the student who is the child of the student. The student is the child of the student who is the parent of the participant. The participant is in the City and the Assistant is the child of the student.
confOf#Volunteer: The volunteer is the parent of the person who is the child of the author. The assistant is the parent of the person who writes the Contribution. The Contribution deals with the topic Thing.
confOf#Regular: The Participant is a member of the Regular and is the parent of the Participant. The Participant is a child of the Regular and the Participant is a child of the Participant.
confOf#Author: The author is the parent of the child of Chair PC and the child of Thing. He also writes.
